<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="61" type="remarks">
<paragraph pageId="8" pageNumber="61">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="8" pageNumber="61">
<bibRefCitation author="Grisebach, AHR" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin de la Societe Botanique de France" pageId="9" pageNumber="62" refId="B11" refString="Grisebach, AHR, 1844. Spicilegium florae rumelicae et bithynicae: exhibens synopsin plantarum. Vol 2. F Vieweg et filium, Brunsvigae." title="Spicilegium florae rumelicae et bithynicae: exhibens synopsin plantarum. Vol 2. F Vieweg et filium, Brunsvigae." year="1844">Grisebach (1844</bibRefCitation>
: 448) described 
<taxonomicName class="Liliopsida" family="Gramineae" genus="Bromus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" infraspecific-rank="sect." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Bromus" order="Poales" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="section" section="Stenobromus">Bromus sect. Stenobromus</taxonomicName>
including 
<taxonomicName family="Poaceae" genus="B." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. maximus" order="Poales" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" rank="species" species="maximus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="61">B. maximus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Desf., 
<taxonomicName family="Poaceae" genus="B." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. madritensis" order="Poales" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" rank="species" species="madritensis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="61">B. madritensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L., 
<taxonomicName family="Poaceae" genus="B." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. tectorum" order="Poales" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" rank="species" species="tectorum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="61">B. tectorum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L. and 
<taxonomicName family="Poaceae" genus="B." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. sterilis" order="Poales" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" rank="species" species="sterilis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="61">B. sterilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L. 
<bibRefCitation author="Hackel, E" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin de la Societe Botanique de France" pageId="9" pageNumber="62" refId="B12" refString="Hackel, E, 1887. Gramineae. In: Engler A, Prantl K (Eds) Die Natuerlichen Planzenfmilien. 2(2): 1-130. Wihelm Engelmann, Leipzig. http://bibdigital.rjb.csic.es/spa/Libro.php?Libro=1636&amp;Pagina=1" title="Gramineae. In: Engler A, Prantl K (Eds) Die Natuerlichen Planzenfmilien. 2 (2): 1 - 130. Wihelm Engelmann, Leipzig. http: // bibdigital. rjb. csic. es / spa / Libro. php? Libro = 1636 &amp; Pagina = 1" year="1887">Hackel (1887</bibRefCitation>
: 75) described 
<taxonomicName authority="subg. Stenobromus" family="Poaceae" genus="B." infraspecific-rank="subg." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B." order="Poales" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" rank="genus" subGenus="Stenobromus">B. subg. Stenobromus</taxonomicName>
including only two species: 
<taxonomicName family="Poaceae" genus="B." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. tectorum" order="Poales" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" rank="species" species="tectorum">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="61">B. tectorum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L. and 
<taxonomicName family="Poaceae" genus="B." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B. sterilis" order="Poales" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" rank="species" species="sterilis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="61">B. sterilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L and gave 
<taxonomicName class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Anisantha" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Anisantha" order="Poales" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" phylum="Magnoliophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="61">Anisantha</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
K. Koch as a synonym. Afterwards, some other species were included. Until now, 
<taxonomicName authority="subg. Stenobromus" family="Poaceae" genus="B." infraspecific-rank="subg." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B." order="Poales" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" rank="genus" subGenus="Stenobromus">B. subg. Stenobromus</taxonomicName>
has been used in some works (
<bibRefCitation author="Stebbins, GL" journalOrPublisher="Botanische Jahrbuecher fuer Systematik, Pflanzengeschichte und Pflanzengeographie" pageId="10" pageNumber="63" pagination="411 - 425" refId="B29" refString="Stebbins, GL, 1981. Chromosomes and evolution in the genus Bromus (Gramineae). Botanische Jahrbuecher fuer Systematik, Pflanzengeschichte und Pflanzengeographie 102 (1-4): 411 - 425" title="Chromosomes and evolution in the genus Bromus (Gramineae)." volume="102" year="1981">Stebbins 1981</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Acedo, C" pageId="9" pageNumber="62" refId="B1" refString="Acedo, C, Llamas, F, 1999. The genus Bromus L. (Poaceae) in the Iberian Peninsula. Phaneogamarum Monographiae. J.Cramer, Berlin." title="The genus Bromus L. (Poaceae) in the Iberian Peninsula. Phaneogamarum Monographiae. J. Cramer, Berlin." year="1999">Acedo and Llamas 1999</bibRefCitation>
) because there is no correct name available for this taxon at subgenus level. As a consequence, 
<taxonomicName authority="subg. Stenobromus" family="Poaceae" genus="B." infraspecific-rank="subg." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B." order="Poales" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" rank="genus" subGenus="Stenobromus">B. subg. Stenobromus</taxonomicName>
is treated as a new combination at new rank because a potential basionym exists, 
<taxonomicName family="Poaceae" genus="B." infraspecific-rank="sect." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="B." order="Poales" pageId="8" pageNumber="61" rank="section" section="Stenobromus">B. sect. Stenobromus</taxonomicName>
, applying to the same taxon ICN Art. 41.4.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="8" pageNumber="61">This subgenus is variable enough to have two sections:</paragraph>
